Reviewing feature support across different object-oriented languages:
Notes:
- Interfaces are supported by multiple languages, but its important to consider
  whether the language you are using supports multiple inheritance.
- Depending on the features you need for programming, different languages will
  offer different benefits.
----------------------
- General OO Design Pattern and Practices

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|Languag|Inheritan|Typing    |Call to     |Private    |Abstract      |Interfaces    |
|e      |ce       |          |super       |Methods    |Classes       |              |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|Java   |Single   |static    |super       |Yes        |Yes           |Yes           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|C#     |Single   |static    |base        |Yes        |Yes           |Yes           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|VB.NET |Single   |static    |MyBase      |Yes        |Yes           |Yes           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|Obj-C  |Single   |static/   |super       |No         |No            |Protocols     |
|       |         |dynamic   |            |           |              |              |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|C++    |Multiple |static    |name of cla |Yes        |Yes           |Abstract      |
|       |         |          |ss::        |           |              |Class         |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|Ruby   |Mix-ins  |dynamic   |super       |Yes        |n/a           |n/a           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|JScript|Prototype|dynamic   |n/a         |Yes        |n/a           |n/a           |
+-------+---------+----------+------------+-----------+--------------+--------------|
